{
  "stem": "21437.8",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think that I was-- first, the most important thing was that I responded to the hope within me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is that I hoped and prayed that some members of my family would have survived.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Secondly, I realized, as well, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that I-- that there is a lot around me, a lot of joy, a lot of positiveness at that stage.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even the joyous response, when the Russian soldiers were going through the town, which people, survivors, apparently, girls, lady survivors, apparently, suffered sometimes at their hands.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was nothing like this happening with those that we have met.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I think straightaway-- maybe that's part of the nature, the human nature-- I straightaway regretted, and, sort of, I-- I realized I had certain skills, although I was already 17.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And yet, I was only 17, and I really had to think very hard, what am I going to do?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was suddenly free.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, how do you handle freedom, if you don't know what it means for six years?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You don't have-- you didn't learn even those social skills and graces that you learn at school whilst you are doing certain things.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't have any of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, I had to-- I had to grow up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think I grew up in the next few days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because I felt a lot of things were filling my body, which, let's say, I felt, you know, you can say, I could reach out and touch those feelings, which, in a way, I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "While, on the other hand, there was like a deadening, you know, a fear, when I felt I could literally-- just like when they were giving me the number, I could taste the fear, you know?",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
